  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7123317/" class="title-link">简而不陋，以史通今</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7123317"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Stewart/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1018146-30.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Stewart/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">锡兵</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-10-09"
      class="main-meta">2014-10-09 17:04:58</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7123317_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本书中文版2013年7月在香港发行，在随后的香港书市上闹出了丑闻，被读者发现某些册去除了对中国政府的负面评价。稍后，出版方出来澄清说，有删节的是少量印刷、专供书展之用的样书，如有误购可以换回原版。虽然不曾明言，大费周章印删节版大概是想打入内地市场。现在一年过去了...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7123317/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7123317_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7123317_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





